rity:</b> {!relatedTo.BMCServiceDesk__FKPriority__r.Name} <br></br><b>Queue:</b> {!relatedTo.BMCServiceDesk__Queue__c}<br></br><div style="display:{!IF(not(isblank(relatedTo.BMCServiceDesk__FKOpenBy__c  )), '', 'none')}"> <b>Staff:</b> {!relatedTo.BMCServiceDesk__FKOpenBy__r.Name}<br></br></div><br></br><b>Additional Details:</b><br></br><apex:outputField value="{!relatedto.BMC_RF_Text_I__c}"/></messaging:htmlEmailBody></messaging:emailTemplate>